api_list.name: room classify
api_list.description: This endpoint classifies the room type of a photo.

api_list.name: pricing
api_list.description: This call is identical to the /house2vec endpoint, except it does not return the house2vec embedding.  This call returns a predicted value based on only your photos.

api_list.name: house2vec
api_list.description: Use the FoxyNet image feature vector to improve the accuracy of your existing valuation and machine learning models.  House2Vec is a batching API call. you can upload up to 25 images in the urls key. The more images you pass, the more accurate we have observed results.
